llama3.1.reason: Saeed Akhtar Mirza being the director of Mohan Joshi Hazir Ho! was stated as a fact by Saeed himself speaking with The Indian Express, but it contradicts with his own description in the other contexts which state that he made notable parallel films such as Mohan Joshi Hazir Ho! and others, implying that he created them, not directed.
